      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_3",
        "observed_type": "section_header",
        "canon_role": "section_header",
        "text": "YOUR MONEY",
        "bbox": [
          0.03696857291065269,
          0.0478670628767953,
          0.6099815223758538,
          0.10912698351171593
        ],
        "order": 4
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_41",
        "observed_type": "picture",
        "canon_role": "picture",
        "text": "",
        "bbox": [
          0.2187455229932495,
          0.12156543227099868,
          1.0,
          0.7383364507550706
        ],
        "order": 5
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_4",
        "observed_type": "section_header",
        "canon_role": "section_header",
        "text": "A NEW year is the prime time to get into healthier habits - including saving for the future.",
        "bbox": [
          0.0314232865807572,
          0.12351190472223411,
          0.21256931962688294,
          0.15261627883924192
        ],
        "order": 6
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_5",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "According to financial information website Moneyfacts, the choice of cash savings deals on the market reached the highest point in December since its records started in 2007. More than 2,000 products were available, so there's a lot to unpick.",
        "bbox": [
          0.029574860560076868,
          0.15401785710318633,
          0.21256931962688294,
          0.1845930231524688
        ],
        "order": 7
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_7",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "taking your first steps into the world of investment, Clare Francis, director of savings and investments at Barclays Smart Investor, above, has tips to help grow a handy pot of cash:",
        "bbox": [
          0.029574866413434646,
          0.26162790698319016,
          0.21256932038165804,
          0.312499999993554
        ],
        "order": 10
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_8",
        "observed_type": "section_header",
        "canon_role": "section_header",
        "text": "1 Co a beage stick",
        "bbox": [
          0.03142329412613783,
          0.3168604659965983,
          0.18484288021150846,
          0.34598214307738845
        ],
        "order": 11
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_10",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "\"The importance of a well-structured budget really cannot be overstated,\" says Clare.",
        "bbox": [
          0.02947247471758439,
          0.3430059525943099,
          0.21274477931266525,
          0.3736463788853614
        ],
        "order": 12
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_9",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "She suggests reviewing your monthly income and outgoings to identify areas where you can cut back on non-essential spending.",
        "bbox": [
          0.029574859038171412,
          0.37354651180492726,
          0.21256932038165804,
          0.4127906974852859
        ],
        "order": 13
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_11",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "\"The money you save can be used to pay off debts, moved into a savings account, or even invested for your future,\" Clare adds.",
        "bbox": [
          0.029574860560076868,
          0.4113372093319958,
          0.21256931787423297,
          0.4521329363273616
        ],
        "order": 14
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_12",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "\"By taking a proactive approach to your budgeting, you not only ensure that every pound is working as hard as possible for you, but that you also cultivate a mindset for long-term financial success.\"",
        "bbox": [
          0.029574865897414968,
          0.4533730159698046,
          0.21256932038165804,
          0.5101744182096076
        ],
        "order": 15
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_13",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "There are plenty of free budgeting tools available online that could help, such as the budget planner from the government-backed MoneyHelper service at moneyhelper.org.uk.",
        "bbox": [
          0.029574863455948595,
          0.5116279071769885,
          0.21256931962688294,
          0.5610465112823138
        ],
        "order": 16
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_14",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "It takes about 10 minutes to complete and can give you a fresh outlook and new understanding of your cash.",
        "bbox": [
          0.029574861992543902,
          0.5610119047464587,
          0.21256931962688294,
          0.6002906973157124
        ],
        "order": 17
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_15",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "\"You don't need to have all your life goals nailed down perfectly, but having a rough idea of what youre aiming for and how much money you'll need is helpful,\" says Clare.",
        "bbox": [
          0.029574862559980607,
          0.6322051013162715,
          0.21266849777838157,
          0.6817956349820871
        ],
        "order": 18
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_17",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "\"It provides a useful starting point to weigh up the best options available to you.",
        "bbox": [
          0.029487847848624543,
          0.6816860465776353,
          0.21256931612661453,
          0.7124429497927258
        ],
        "order": 19
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_16",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Many people keep all their cash in savings accounts.",
        "bbox": [
          0.031423292447257854,
          0.7107558138256973,
          0.21256931298359846,
          0.7311507937144682
        ],
        "order": 20
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_18",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "But Clare suggests that if you've got money you can afford to put away for the longer term, perhaps for five years or more, then investing could be worth considering.",
        "bbox": [
          0.029574860560076868,
          0.7311046511561234,
          0.21256931787423297,
          0.7808358218769148
        ],
        "order": 21
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_21",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "money if only they felt more confident funds, which may be a good place to if they have a background in finance or experience in the investment field.",
        "bbox": [
          0.21996305647890915,
          0.747023809594151,
          0.7837338199844298,
          0.767441860227534
        ],
        "order": 22
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_35",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Financial Conduct Authorityhas a warning list of firms on its website as well as a financial services register of firms and people involved in regulated",
        "bbox": [
          0.785582254275419,
          0.7470238097394998,
          0.9704251297859272,
          0.7892441861743028
        ],
        "order": 23
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_19",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Money held in investments may potentially see stronger growth over the longer-term than savings held in cash.",
        "bbox": [
          0.029574860560076868,
          0.7805059526124785,
          0.21256932038165804,
          0.8183139533046294
        ],
        "order": 25
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_23",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Choosing where and how to invest money can feel daunting, which may for some people be a barrier to moving some of their money from cash savings",
        "bbox": [
          0.21996302787773805,
          0.8154069768475314,
          0.40110906160162096,
          0.8561507934422706
        ],
        "order": 27
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_31",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "investment scams starting on social media, it is important to \"sense check\"",
        "bbox": [
          0.5970425130554559,
          0.8182043650552508,
          0.7800369632846553,
          0.8373015874730516
        ],
        "order": 28
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_27",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "fund with a level of risk that you're",
        "bbox": [
          0.4085027771728309,
          0.8182043652668863,
          0.5914972274020305,
          0.8284883718624979
        ],
        "order": 29
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_20",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "But people putting money into investments will need to be comfortable with the risks and be aware that they could potentially get less money back than they put in.",
        "bbox": [
          0.029574864084097263,
          0.8211805553706466,
          0.21256931962688294,
          0.8706395346350269
        ],
        "order": 30
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_37",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "is a good habit to get into, so is investing regularly, says Clare.",
        "bbox": [
          0.7871574885570187,
          0.8531746032487785,
          0.8927911253797084,
          0.8853401364912645
        ],
        "order": 32
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_32",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Consider whether claims about high investment returns, for example, seem",
        "bbox": [
          0.5970425191552707,
          0.8575581396563976,
          0.7800369693844703,
          0.8779761905993156
        ],
        "order": 33
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_39",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Analysis by Barclays indicates that many savers could be missing out on potentially higher returns.",
        "bbox": [
          0.029574859038171412,
          0.869186046760322,
          0.16081330675426755,
          0.9099702380117836
        ],
        "order": 34
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_29",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Clare says: \"Our recent research found that a quarter of Brits are now turning to social media, community messaging information about investing.\"",
        "bbox": [
          0.40850276846615463,
          0.8851686505932959,
          0.5914972240363496,
          0.9374999997886437
        ],
        "order": 36
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_33",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "It is crucial to keep in mind as well that fraudsters may use deepfake videos or other bogus information to give the false impression that an investment scheme has been endorsed",
        "bbox": [
          0.5988909404316505,
          0.8880813954340138,
          0.780036972877037,
          0.9374999998593171
        ],
        "order": 37
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_38",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "think you need a",
        "bbox": [
          0.7874306839131097,
          0.8923611111816736,
          0.8835489827535573,
          0.9026162790633215
        ],
        "order": 38
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_25",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Pound cost averaging can help smooth out overall returns and reduce the risk they are afraid of making prevents them from taking",
        "bbox": [
          0.1718835205915159,
          0.8981682146401542,
          0.2643253221326431,
          0.9593253969749692
        ],
        "order": 39
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_24",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "It estimates that 13 million UK adults hold £430billion of possible investments\" in cash savings, so they could be missing out on a lot of extra",
        "bbox": [
          0.029521562636494095,
          0.9098837210170759,
          0.160813309157225,
          0.9680232554552471
        ],
        "order": 40
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_34",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "If youre unsure about a particular firm, remember that regulator the",
        "bbox": [
          0.5988909436818045,
          0.9461805555267756,
          0.780036972122262,
          0.9680232555834278
        ],
        "order": 41
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_26",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "fact many providers offer diversification and invest in a mixture of cash, bonds and shares but the levels of risk vary, explains Clare.",
